Energize the capture crystal! Now take it, Gloria!

336
00:26:16,320 --> 00:26:20,320
And run and place it in the Quinoa lost chamber to capture Carmen Sandiego!

337
00:26:29,920 --> 00:26:35,680
Where in Time is Carmen Sandiego would last for two seasons, for a total of 115 episodes.

338
00:26:35,680 --> 00:26:38,480
Since the conclusion of Where in the World is Carmen Sandiego,

339
00:26:38,480 --> 00:26:43,680
the titular character has continued her cultural relevancy through consistent video game releases.

340
00:26:43,680 --> 00:26:47,680
Carmen Sandiego was also given a fourth television series on Netflix,

341
00:26:47,680 --> 00:26:50,720
which premiered in 2019 and ran for four seasons.

342
00:26:50,720 --> 00:26:54,640
This animated show incorporated elements from the original 90s animation,

343
00:26:54,640 --> 00:26:58,320
the computer games, and of course, the hit PBS game show.

