Over the decades, geographical changes have made much of the trivia featured on

346
00:27:11,360 --> 00:27:14,880
Where in the World is Carmen Sandiego outdated and incorrect.

347
00:27:14,880 --> 00:27:17,600
Fans can find VHS rips of the series on YouTube,

348
00:27:17,600 --> 00:27:19,920
but there have been no official releases of the show,

349
00:27:19,920 --> 00:27:23,440
and likely won't be due to the now factual inaccuracies.

350
00:27:23,520 --> 00:27:26,320
The game show is well remembered for its elaborate theming,

351
00:27:26,320 --> 00:27:29,760
high energy, production value, and talented cast.

352
00:27:29,760 --> 00:27:33,280
It is considered not only one of PBS's greatest children shows,

353
00:27:33,280 --> 00:27:36,160
but one of the greatest game shows created for children.

354
00:27:36,160 --> 00:27:39,760
Impressive considering it aired in the golden age of children's game shows.

355
00:27:40,320 --> 00:27:45,360
Above all, the show had a very specific goal of educating children on geography,

356
00:27:45,360 --> 00:27:49,760
a goal that it achieved and surpassed, resulting in not just education,

357
00:27:49,760 --> 00:27:52,800
but celebration of the world and its cultures.

358
00:27:52,800 --> 00:27:56,800
All of this wrapped inside a humorous, non-stop detective adventure.

359
00:27:56,800 --> 00:27:58,960
It is no wonder that the show was a hit,

